ResultDataSet.Identifier: Routing Protocols\RLDP-RSVP LSP Results\SVP Sub-LSP Results
ResultDataSet.Name: RSVP Sub-LSP Results

RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.SqlString: SELECT AllDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', RsvpSubLspResults.Direction AS 'Direction', RsvpSubLspResults.SrcIpAddr AS 'Source IP Address', RsvpSubLspResults.TunnelId AS 'Tunnel ID', RsvpSubLspResults.ExtendedTunnelId AS 'Extended Tunnel ID', RsvpSubLspResults.DstIpAddr AS 'Destination IP Address', RsvpSubLspResults.SubLspState AS 'Sub LSP State', RsvpSubLspResults.Label AS 'Label', RsvpSubLspResults.P2MpId AS 'P2MP ID', RsvpSubLspResults.SubGroupOriginatorId AS 'SubGroup Originator ID', RsvpSubLspResults.SubGroupId AS 'SubGroup ID' FROM RsvpSubLspResults, AllDevice, RsvpRouterConfig, RsvpLspResults WHERE (RsvpSubLspResults.ParentProtocolConfig = RsvpLspResults.SecHandle AND RsvpSubLspResults.PortName = RsvpLspResults.PortName AND RsvpLspResults.ParentHnd = RsvpRouterConfig.Handle AND RsvpRouterConfig.ParentHnd = AllDevice.Handle AND RsvpSubLspResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND AllDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RsvpRouterConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RsvpLspResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId )
RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.Name: RealTimeResultGroupDefinition 10
